the B range). So, to use KU=E2=80=99s grade-point conversion scale to figur=
e out my new percentage-based grading scale, I need to pay attention to mid=
dle percentages, not minimum percentages. My old grading scale had 95 in th=
e middle of the A range, 85 in the middle of the B range, and so on. I=E2=
=80=99ll keep these as the middle percentages in my new grading scale:</p><=
