pan></td><td><span></span></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Now, there are just =
a couple of further decisions I have to make. First, what should the thresh=
old between D=E2=80=93 and F be? For consistency with my old grading scale =
and for consistency between D=E2=80=93 and the other minus grades under my =
new grading scale, I=E2=80=99ll make it 60.</p></div></div><div id=3D"secti=
on-three" class=3D"container"><div><p>Second, should a student whose percen=
tage is equal to a threshold percentage get the letter grade just above it,=
 or just below? For reasons of charity, I prefer to award the letter grade =
just above it. So, these thresholds are actually the minimum percentages fo=
